Get all Hotels
curl -X GET http://localhost:3000/api/hotels

Get a specific hotel by ID:
curl -X GET http://localhost:3000/api/hotels/{hotelId}

Create a new hotel object:
curl -X POST http://localhost:3000/api/hotels -H "Content-Type: application/json" -d '{
  "name": "Parkway Inn",
  "location": "Ikeja, LA",
  "rating": 5
}'

Update a hotel by ID:
curl -X PUT http://localhost:3000/api/hotels/{hotelId} -H "Content-Type: application/json" -d '{
  "name": "Parkway Inn",
  "location": "Ikeja, LA",
  "rating": 3
}'

ROOM ENDPOINTS
Get all rooms for a specific hotel:
curl -X GET http://localhost:3000/api/hotels/{hotelId}/rooms

Get a specific room by ID:
curl -X GET http://localhost:3000/api/hotels/{hotelId}/rooms/{roomId}

Create a new room for a specific hotel:
curl -X POST http://localhost:3000/api/hotels/{hotelId}/rooms -H "Content-Type: application/json" -d '{
    "number": "103",
    "type": "Suite",
    "price": 250,
    "available": true
}'

Update a room by ID:
curl -X PUT http://localhost:3000/api/hotels/{hotelId}/rooms/{roomId} -H "Content-Type: application/json" -d '{
  "type": "Suite",
  "price": 300,
  "available": false
}'

Delete a Room by ID:
curl -X DELETE http://localhost:3000/api/hotels/{hotelId}/rooms/{roomId}

BOOKINGS
Creating a Booking for a Room:
curl -X POST http://localhost:3000/api/hotels/66990683bf4526dfcb7e6161/rooms/669907a9bf4526dfcb7e616a/bookings -H "Content-Type: application/json" -d '{
    "user": "6697a67cc909f14287deedef",
    "guestEmail": "oluwasegun@delifted.com.ng",
    "checkInDate": "2024-10-14",
    "checkOutDate": "2024-10-14"
}'

Get all Bookings on the platform
curl -X GET http://localhost:3000/api/bookings

Get all Bookings for a specific room:
curl -X GET http://localhost:3000/api/hotels/{hotelId}/rooms/{roomId}/bookings

Get a specific Booking by ID:
curl -X GET http://localhost:3000/api/hotels/{hotelId}/rooms/{roomId}/bookings/{bookingId}

Delete a booking by ID:
curl -X DELETE http://localhost:3000/api/hotels/{hotelId}/rooms/{roomId}/bookings/{bookingId}


USER
User Registration:
curl -X POST http://localhost:3000/api/users/register -H "Content-Type: application/json" -d '{
  "username": "testuser",
  "email": "testuser@example.com",
  "password": "testpassword"
}'

User login:
curl -X POST http://localhost:3000/api/users/login -H "Content-Type: application/json" -d '{
  "email": "testuser@example.com",
  "password": "testpassword"
}'
